ComicInfo.Title: Peril On Parallel Planets!; Out Of Time: the Missing Chapter
ComicInfo.Writer: David Zimmerman,Gary Carlson,James Chambers,James Chambers,Gary Carlson
ComicInfo.Summary: The Dragon arrives in 1981, where The Whiz Kids believe he's the menace known as "The Timebomber". After explanations, they all travel into the future to "The Godrealm", where it seems every hero from both Earths are in battle! When The Blitz of Earth-B arrives, Dragon convinces him they can change time and prevent utter disaster if they travel back to April 29, 1969-- which they do...
